a live studio audience.

00:05.821 --> 00:08.289
Oh, Sammy, look who's here.

00:08.357 --> 00:09.591
Harry the Hat.

00:09.658 --> 00:10.798
Aw, man, how many times

00:10.799 --> 00:12.994
am I gonna have to chase
that guy out of here?

00:12.995 --> 00:15.330
Grab your wallets, everybody.

00:15.397 --> 00:17.365
Hello, Harry.
Hey, Sam.

00:17.366 --> 00:19.984
What you doing, trying to
sell some bogus watches,

00:19.985 --> 00:22.587
some knock off's to my customers
and try to cheat 'em?

00:22.588 --> 00:24.122
