00:32.865 --> 00:36.668
Hey. Sounds like a
Rolex, doesn't it?

00:36.736 --> 00:38.970
Oh, look at that-
still ticking, too.

00:39.037 --> 00:41.606
Uh, Sam...

00:41.607 --> 00:42.557
Hey, do me a favour.

00:42.558 --> 00:44.025
Just, just take
your bogus goods

00:44.026 --> 00:45.727
and peddle them
someplace else, will ya?

00:45.728 --> 00:48.258
So Harry, are you interested
in buying the watch?

00:48.297 --> 00:52.066
No, but I think my
friend Sam might be.

