02:33.285 --> 02:34.352
Yeah. That's right.

02:34.353 --> 02:35.786
You know, this time tomorrow

02:35.787 --> 02:37.522
when Gary's still decorating
Olde Towne Tavern,

02:37.523 --> 02:40.024
this place's gonna be open,
people are gonna be flooding in.

02:40.025 --> 02:42.255
That's a good idea, Sam.
You're damned right.

02:42.261 --> 02:45.162
Hey, finally, for the first
time, St. Patrick's Day,

02:45.163 --> 02:46.898
Cheers is gonna do
more business

02:46.899 --> 02:48.332
than Gary's Olde Towne Tavern.

02:48.333 --> 02:50.501
Yes!
Yes!

02:50.502 --> 02:51.970
I wouldn't be too
sure about that.

02:51.971 --> 02:53.238
