09:37.693 --> 09:41.228
♪ 'Twas a baby's crib
that floated... ♪

09:41.296 --> 09:42.964
No! No! No! No!
No baby's crib!

09:43.031 --> 09:44.298
Stop it.

09:44.299 --> 09:46.033
Here, get the hell
out of here, will you?

09:46.034 --> 09:47.568
Take your money.
Go on, get out.

09:47.636 --> 09:49.436
Go to hell.

09:53.909 --> 09:55.993
Let's face it;
It's over, huh?

09:56.061 --> 09:58.663
Might as well tally up and
see what we've got there.

09:58.664 --> 10:00.214
Yeah, Woody, what's the total?

10:00.215 --> 10:04.017
Well...
(adding machine keys clicking)

10:04.085 --> 10:07.087
