10:16.898 --> 10:18.549
Hey guys, bad news.

10:18.616 --> 10:20.117
I just came from Gary's.

10:20.185 --> 10:22.386
He's raking in the money,
hand over fist.

10:22.387 --> 10:23.921
And then again why shouldn't he?

10:23.922 --> 10:25.912
I mean, he's charging
five bucks a beer.

10:28.093 --> 10:29.977
