Well, let's get it over with.

11:44.103 --> 11:45.937
Yeah, yeah, all right, Gary.
Go on. Go on. Go on.

11:45.938 --> 11:49.140
Okay, I want to see
some big smiles.

11:50.008 --> 11:51.976
Ladies and gentlemen,

11:52.044 --> 11:55.679
Gary's Olde Towne Tavern has the
privilege of presenting an act

11:55.748 --> 11:59.016
