13:32.210 --> 13:35.012
I thought we were
a lot tighter the second show.

13:37.415 --> 13:40.101
How am I ever gonna show my face
in here again?

13:40.168 --> 13:42.986
Paul, it's not your
face that's burned into my memory.

13:46.374 --> 13:48.876
You know, I kind of found
the whole thing,

13:48.943 --> 13:51.111
uh, quite exhilarating.

13:52.481 --> 13:53.830
Exhilarating?

13:53.898 --> 13:57.768
I meant humiliating.

13:57.836 --> 14:00.537
It was really humiliating.

14:02.073 --> 14:04.241
Uh, guys, you've been really
good to me,

14:04.309 --> 14:05.776
so I'm gonna be good to you.

14:05.843 --> 14:06.910
