14:06.978 --> 14:09.530
Yeah, that's real funny.

14:09.598 --> 14:10.947
That's real funny stuff.

14:10.948 --> 14:12.516
I'll tell you something, man.

14:12.517 --> 14:14.785
I'm gonna get you- I don't
care how long it takes,

14:14.786 --> 14:17.054
how much money it costs,
how many lives are lost,

14:17.055 --> 14:19.523
I'm gonna get you, Gary,
once and for all.

14:19.591 --> 14:20.690
Oh, I hope not

14:20.691 --> 14:22.326
because I'm still shaking
from that terrifying

14:22.327 --> 14:23.494
five-dollar-beer prank.

14:23.495 --> 14:26.763
Yeah, well, I'm still
gonna get you.

14:26.831 --> 14:28.465
Sammy, let's just give it up.

14:28.533 --> 14:29.750
No! Never!

14:29.818 --> 14:31.652
I tell you
I'm gonna get that guy.

